The CLIMEX Compare Locations model simulates a species population response to climate on a weekly timescale; tracking the potential for population growth during favourable seasons, and population decreases during the stressful seasons. CLIMEX calculates an annual Growth Index (GIA) to describe the potential for population growth as a function of weekly soil moisture and temperature during favourable conditions (Eq. 1).1\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
